docs.text: Bac à sable ¶ Code ¶ """ Bubble sort """ def bubble_sort ( items ): for i in range ( len ( items )): for j in range ( len ( items ) - 1 - i ): if items [ j ] > items [ j + 1 ]: items [ j ], items [ j + 1 ] = items [ j + 1 ], items [ j ] Test ¶ Test latex f(x)=2x f(x)=2x \frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!} = \binom{n}{k} \frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!} = \binom{n}{k}
